$interpreted: : Some days later...
Beyata: It's been a long time, Master Orisuke. Did you come to see me because of the bidding?
Orisuke: Oh? How did you know? Has word made it around the entire Fog Sect already?
Orisuke: Y-Yes, I got news today that the owner of Eika Textiles was killed. Something about getting involved with the wrong people...
Orisuke: And so the Alliance made me their official clothier!
Beyata: Really!? That's amazing! Congratulations!
Orisuke: Yes, it all seems wonderful... and yet I can't shake the feeling that something strange happened behind the scenes.
Beyata: At least you got the contract! You should be happy!
Beyata: Your business is about to boom! I can feel it! So... do you still remember the promise you made?
Orisuke: Of course! The moment the Alliance pays me their advance, I will talk to your boss about ending your contract.
Beyata: You'll definitely come free me, right? No matter what happens?
Orisuke: ...I promise. No matter what, I won't let you stay here alone!
Beyata: Even if you die?
Orisuke: Uh... what?
Beyata: Promise me that even if you die, and your whole family dies...
Beyata: you'll still arrange for someone else to come free me.
Orisuke: ...I-I promise! I'll free you no matter what!
Beyata: Yay~! I feel a lot better hearing that~
Beyata: Life is but a dream, isn't it~ I'm so lucky!
Beyata: (What day is it today? W-Who am I? Where am I?)
Rich Guest: Hey, quit playin' dead! I'm not satisfied yet!
Beyata: (Oh, right! I'm Beyata, and I'm going to become Master Orisuke's woman...)
Beyata: Hehehe~
Rich Guest: Seems like you can enjoy my little games, too. Guess it was a good idea puttin' down money to make you my own.
Beyata: M-Money? Your own? What do you mean?
Rich Guest: I guess I might as well tell you.
Rich Guest: I put down money to buy you from that boss of yours, so you can be my permanent plaything.
Rich Guest: It's an honor, so you must be pretty excited.
Beyata: ...B-But, how... why...
Rich Guest: Are you not excited?
Beyata: N-No, it's not that! I'm just... very surprised! The excitement will come!
Rich Guest: Hmph~ Women...
Rich Guest: You know, you don't look happy in the slightest.
Rich Guest: I thought you'd be over the moon.
Beyata: ...Yagh, mngh, please don't─
Beyata: (I can't deny him, it'll make the boss mad... and yet, aren't I the boss's number one?)
Beyata: (I can't die here, I'll just give the boss even more trouble!)
Beyata: (And I still have Master Orisuke's promise!)
Beyata: ─Get away from me!
Rich Guest: Whoa, what gives you the right!?
Beyata: (A little closer, a little closer...)
Beyata: Do you know how difficult it is... to make dreams come true?
Beyata: I will not──die here today!!
Guesthouse Boss: What in the world...
Guesthouse Boss: I thought, after that day, you were reborn. I thought you truly saw who you were meant to be.
Guesthouse Boss: Never would I think you meddle in my business and injure a guest!! Get her!!
Beyata: ──Yaaaaaaaagh!!
Cruel Staff: Good think he is barely hurt, otherwise I'd own you for ten lives over!
Guesthouse Boss: And now you've ruined your deal with our guest!
Guesthouse Boss: Do you know how much money that deal would have gotten me and the guesthouse!?
Beyata: ......
Guesthouse Boss: You've truly disappointed me, Bluebird.
Guesthouse Boss: There are new young, obedient girls showing up on Hot Spring Street every day. We don't need you anymore.
Beyata: What!? I thought I was the best... your top girl! You said it!!
Cruel Staff: And so you thought that gave you license to hurt a guest!? Know your place, Beyata!
Beyata: ...You're abandoning me just like my grandfather did... nobody wants me...
Guesthouse Boss: ...Let her stay here alone for a bit. I can't have her going crazy on me, it's not worth it.
Beyata: Good thing I took it back...
Beyata: I'm so worthless... my grandfather, and now the boss... they've all thrown me away.
Beyata: Master Orisuke was right.
Beyata: I don't belong here. I don't belong to the boss... I'm not a plaything...
Beyata: I only belong to Master Orisuke. I am his Bluebird...
Beyata: Master Orisuke is the only one who can bring me happiness.
